ning to end. Understand the entire user journey to provide the right information in the right place at the right time.","position":{"start":{"line":67,"column":1,"offset":3410},"end":{"line":67,"column":214,"offset":3623}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":67,"column":1,"offset":3410},"end":{"line":67,"column":214,"offset":3623}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Strategies to try","position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":3,"offset":3627},"end":{"line":69,"column":20,"offset":3644}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":1,"offset":3625},"end":{"line":69,"column":22,"offset":3646}}},{"type":"text","value":"\nFrame each task as a conversation. Imagine you are sitting in a room with your user, and write out the conversation you might have with them to help them accomplish their task. This activity can help in several different ways:","position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":22,"offset":3646},"end":{"line":70,"column":227,"offset":3873}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":1,"offset":3625},"end":{"line":70,"column":227,"offset":3873}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"It helps you write in a natural and conversational way, which can inform and improve the content you use in the interface.","position":{"start":{"line":71,"column":3,"offset":3876},"end":{"line":71,"column":125,"offset":3998}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":71,"column":1,"offset":3874},"end":{"line":71,"column":125,"offset":3998}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"It helps you anticipate questions the user might have along the way.","position":{"start":{"line":72,"column":3,"offset":4001},"end":{"line":72,"column"